lead_paragraph: Arsenal midfielder Aaron Ramsey hopes the North London can choke Leicester City's unexpected Premier League title charge after picking up their first win in five matches in Sunday's 2-0 win over Bournemouth.

headline.print_headline: Confident Arsenal Hopes to Stifle Leicester Charge
